snippet: Channing Tatum, one of moviedom’s best hopes for a new male superstar, is working almost nonstop to stand out from Hollywood’s pretty boys.
abstract: Channing Tatum, one of Hollywood's best hopes for a new male superstar, is working hard to stand out from the pretty boys of film, a feat that is becoming increasingly difficult in recent years; Tatum will appear in the comedy 21 Jump Street.
lead_paragraph: Channing Tatum, one of moviedom’s best hopes for a new male superstar, is working almost nonstop to stand out from Hollywood’s pretty boys.

headline.seo: Channing Tatum Works to Be the Next Big Star
headline.main: Making a Leading Man, Many Movies at a Time
